<section class="section section-white" id="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <div class="section-label">FAQ</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked<br>Questions</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Everything you need to know about our services.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list reveal">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q">What areas do you serve?<span class="faq-q-icon"></span></button>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>We serve all locations within 160 km of Pune, including Pimpri, Hinjewadi, Wakad, Baner, Kharadi, Hadapsar, Talegaon, Lonavala, Satara, Ahmednagar, Baramati, Chakan, and surrounding areas. Travel charges may apply for locations beyond 20 km.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q">How far in advance should I book?<span class="faq-q-icon"></span></button>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>We recommend booking at least 3-5 days in advance for small setups and 1-2 weeks for large or luxury events. However, we do accommodate last-minute bookings subject to availability.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q">What is included in the decoration price?<span class="faq-q-icon"></span></button>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>All prices include the cost of materials, setup, and basic styling. Premium add-ons like LED lights, fog machines, neon signs, and flowers may cost extra. Each package clearly lists inclusions and exclusions.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q">Do you offer customization?<span class="faq-q-icon"></span></button>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>Absolutely! Every decoration is tailored to your preferences. We work with you to choose colors, themes, and elements that match your vision. Our AI assistant can help suggest ideas based on your budget and occasion.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q">What is the cancellation policy?<span class="faq-q-icon"></span></button>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>Cancellations made 48+ hours before the event receive a full refund. Cancellations within 24-48 hours receive a 50% refund. Cancellations within 24 hours are non-refundable. Rescheduling is free if done 24+ hours in advance.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q">How long does setup take?<span class="faq-q-icon"></span></button>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>Setup time depends on the package. Small setups take 1-2 hours, medium setups take 2-4 hours, large setups take 4-6 hours, and luxury events may take 8-12 hours or more depending on complexity.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q">Do you accept advance payments?<span class="faq-q-icon"></span></button>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>Yes, we offer flexible payment options: 20% advance to confirm your booking, 50% advance for medium to large setups, or 100% full payment with a special discount. We accept UPI, cards, net banking, and all major payment methods.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

